entries.title_d: We have the area of the Blacklight pirates command staff nailed down, now to find which ship the leader is in. Patrol the assigned area and let your scan systems do the work.
entries.title: Endor system: Patrol for the Blacklight Leader.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < We got him! Proceed with the mission, pilot. >
entries.quest_patrol_d: We will update your patrol and try to keep it away from nearby Blacklight pirates while your sensors are scanning the command ships.
entries.quest_location_d: You are still in a high risk area of a high risk system so no time to relax my friend.
